{"tid":681644,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先有個台仔行埋嚟性騷擾我","createTime":"2018-05-28T08:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T12:35:21.000Z","uid":2155,"like":2512,"dislike":174,"uniUserReply":125,"replies":[{"pid":"be3a2dc460468284dcd7d44332a1d886d60dc04a","tid":681644,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"話說我同frd 去咗台灣<br />\n我個frd 就去左廁所，咁我就企係出面等佢啦<br />\n咁就有個著住supreme 嘅台仔行埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台仔：hi, 你好，你是來旅遊的嗎<br />\n我：是<br />\n台仔：你是港女嗎？<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台仔：我可以帶你四處走走<br />\n台仔：我可以渣你的奶嗎？<br />\n然後我嚇咗一嚇，就跑走咗<br />\n台灣真係充滿厹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe54925af16f2cdead5e0b954c52135aee1e977a","tid":681644,"uid":8379,"like":4737,"dislike":79,"score":4658,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"佢係想講加你line啊？"},{"pid":"9efd39e4548c3263f6dd486eeb05baf516730050","tid":681644,"uid":4859,"like":1451,"dislike":5,"score":1446,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:19:57.000Z","msg":"40分 唔錯"},{"pid":"3f23ba4c002a36d58711147f1b2b0b0dc6407dff","tid":681644,"uid":2155,"like":117,"dislike":810,"score":-693,"quote":{"pid":"fe54925af16f2cdead5e0b954c52135aee1e977a","tid":681644,"uid":8379,"like":4737,"dislike":79,"score":4658,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:18:43.000Z","msg":"佢係想講加你line啊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:19:58.000Z","msg":"加你的line<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌，柒撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我仲講咗句 &quot;變態！&quot;先走"},{"pid":"71e419183e204de0a13f0596692a7c6c831a0fbb","tid":681644,"uid":170044,"like":614,"dislike":3,"score":611,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"你身上穿的supr